{"tid":1501410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發，唔賣個人私隱就用唔到E-道過關","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T13:09:33.000Z","uid":262065,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c67a0907ee0a0bf4a9d0b30e260ff93d46c5da1","tid":1501410,"uid":262065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩經落馬洲口岸返香港時，用e道過關，一插身份證入部機，屏幕就問我同唔同意把我的個人私隱資料（列左好多項.....如身份證號碼等）轉交內地行政用途，有得揀同意和不同意。<br />\n我按左唔同意，部機就通知我e 道服務取消左，之後唔用得e道。<br />\n唔賣資料就唔用得，痴L線，唔好被人揀啦，垃圾！但同行既都冇見到，應該隨機抽人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"aa2e94d2e9d7d8873cdba51471eddc0d1afd95df","tid":1501410,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"會問已經叫好<br />\n你老味你唔係以為佢要order嘅香港政府有咩個人資料唔會送中嘛？"},{"pid":"74c5cd02f4fa6f9bc9f3d5ad6516220ccf5ca587","tid":1501410,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:19:52.000Z","msg":"皇崗定落馬洲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e589eaee8cdd59f20ca9fc56cac6880f1215362c","tid":1501410,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"而家仲上大陸係咪ON9?"},{"pid":"4e3ae84c6d4bfe5f0b3b90550667c06b84abc187","tid":1501410,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"多口問一句，過關有無check手機？"},{"pid":"e481809a6a0577b185bc58d1402c676d146e92c9","tid":1501410,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid